      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like i'm just a glitch in the system or something. i spend all day staring at screens, typing things out, and then i just log off and the world keeps moving like i was never even there. even in this city, it's just silence. if i just... stopped showing up, would anyone even realize i was gone?",
