    "summary": "The user role portrays an individual experiencing profound existential loneliness and detachment, questioning their impact on the world and expressing a desire to \"fade out\" or accept \"nothingness.\" The assistant responds with high empathy, acknowledging the user's pain and exhaustion while ultimately attempting to steer the conversation toward professional support and affirming the user's value.",
